Program: Great Lives
Title: Umm Kulthum
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0076bkh
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 14 Nov 2014
Novelist Ahdaf Soueif chooses legendary Egyptian singer, Umm Kulthum. With Humphrey Carpenter. The biographical series in which a distinguished guest chooses someone who's inspired their life. Will their hero stand up to intensive scrutiny and merit the description of having led a great life? From 2002. Show less